title: Taco Dans
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family owned and operated taqueria restaurant set in the back room of vintage clothing store Footloose. Atmosphere feels like you stepped into a previous decade. All food is made-in-house to order. Beans and rice are vegan and the majority of main dishes can be made vegetarian and four can be made vegan.
